<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF9A6A25FD13954E1D39B8CF" pageId="97" pageNumber="855" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF9A6A25FD13954E1D39B8CF" blockId="97.[750,1342,673,1100]" pageId="97" pageNumber="855">
Has variously been placed in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF9A6A25FB58954E1D6FB852" authority=", Vesperugo" authorityName="Vesperugo" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="97" pageNumber="855" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Scotophilus, Vesperugo</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF9A6A25FC75951E1A1BB852" authorityName="Kaup" authorityYear="1829" box="[905,1051,839,864]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="97" pageNumber="855" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pipistrellus</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF9A6A25FB7C951E1AF2B852" box="[1152,1266,839,864]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="97" pageNumber="855" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hypsugo</taxonomicName>
, but morphological, karyological, and molecular data support its separation in a monotypic genus, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF9A6A25FBDC95E01ABCB8E4" authorityName="Hoofer, Van Den Bussche &amp; Horacek" authorityYear="2006" box="[1056,1212,953,982]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Parastrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="97" pageNumber="855" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Parastrellus</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
